asset.hookText:
See more: http://TheBlaze.com/TV.

An auto mechanic in Tennessee saw a need for an invention, to help broken down cars. What he came up with started an industry now with $15 billion, and the rest is history. This is an "illuminating moment in American history" (as first seen on TheBlaze TV show "Liberty Treehouse").
